Package: qproj
Title: Lightweight Framework for Quarto Analysis Workflows
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
  person("Rujin", "Long", role = c("aut", "cre"),
         email = "rujinlong@example.com")
Description: A lightweight framework for Quarto-based analysis project
  workflows. Provides tools to create and manage sequenced Quarto analysis
  files, with structured data directories and package dependency management
  via pak.
